				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/C%E1%BA%A3m-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-uiwBeq5pOS0xlRMbYlb6Vg">Cảm hứng - 感興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/author-jwIeMxg44qgv_V08xi02Hw">Trần Ngọc Dư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%B1u-th%E1%BB%8B-T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9/poem-bKoaUbR8-1ZxH8NB1YKCaw">Hựu thị Tông Vũ - 又示宗武</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Mai-Th%C3%B4n/poem-WyDPaZUxe3GCT4f2OXM6bA">Mai Thôn - 梅村</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-c%C3%BAc-thu%E1%BB%B7-nguy%E1%BB%87t-t%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-YCX3i6Ujl0-4PFgEYq_QRg">Phú đắc cúc thuỷ nguyệt tại thủ kỳ 2 - 賦得掬水月在手其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u-ca-th%E1%BA%ADp-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-7/poem-xeeBjh-jQHRdIZVACHlllQ">Quỳ Châu ca thập tuyệt cú kỳ 7 - 夔州歌十絕句其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Quy-lai/poem-rDxwNwfRpboJTZeh0QdUsg">Quy lai - 歸來</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-72N6ob4Hsg7Gc-KrAOsrTA">Viên Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-dCpK7Q6s2GPPVO5MWvnenA">Thị đệ - 示弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
